  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposal, by reason of its depth, would restrict the functioning of the service road to the rear, to the detriment of highways safety and functional servicing of the site and neighbouring properties. The development is therefore considered to be contrary to policy T7 (G) of The London Plan (2021), and policies  DM44 and DM45 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013). \r\n",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed development, by reason of its siting in Flood Zones 2 and 3a and local surface water flood zones 3a and 3b, in the absence of an adequate Flood Risk Assessment to assess the future impacts and provide adequate mitigation measures,  would be likely to result in the displacement of water onto adjacent land and fail to provide resilience to flooding, to the detriment of the safety of future occupiers of the application site and adjacent sites, contrary to policy CS1.U of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012), policy SI 12 of The London Plan (2021) and policies DM9 and DM10 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013).\r\n"
